11
00:02:02,340 --> 00:02:03,620
Have you heard this?

12
00:02:06,980 --> 00:02:07,860
At that time,

13
00:02:08,340 --> 00:02:09,539
I thought they

14
00:02:09,900 --> 00:02:11,340
