22
00:02:35,180 --> 00:02:36,420
What do you mean by "when we're free"?

23
00:02:42,020 --> 00:02:42,620
Right.

24
00:02:43,940 --> 00:02:45,020
A friend from the institute

25
00:02:45,100 --> 00:02:45,940
told me

26
00:02:46,740 --> 00:02:48,220
