00:36:44,100 --> 00:36:44,700
Good morning!

591
00:36:45,980 --> 00:36:46,500
Excuse me.

592
00:36:47,140 --> 00:36:48,660
Do you know a place nearby

593
00:36:48,660 --> 00:36:49,620
